WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: 3-MzLZlrTcI

NOTE Language: en

00:00:00.367 --> 00:00:04.713
Malpensa. Milan (Italy) , 26 Aprile 2001.

00:00:10.533 --> 00:00:39.442
At Mother’s arrival, She is covered by flowers.

00:01:09.604 --> 00:01:20.596
Sahaja Yogis welcome Her by singing “Vishwa Vandita” and “Aspettando Lei”

00:06:12.332 --> 00:06:16.015
It’s very heartening to see

00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:20.891
so many of you coming to welcome Me.

00:06:29.625 --> 00:06:34.192
I feel so joyous I can’t express it in words.

00:06:41.077 --> 00:06:45.231
Your love is like the ocean

00:06:45.338 --> 00:06:51.798
which just moves from one person to another.

00:06:59.432 --> 00:07:02.928
It’s so great to come to Italy again.

00:07:39.308 --> 00:07:44.064
Italians have a very large heart.

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:53.466
I have found out that this is like My own country.

00:08:31.099 --> 00:08:39.484
They are here to enjoy love and to enjoy spirituality.

00:08:44.755 --> 00:08:48.654
And they are very spiritual people.

00:08:52.295 --> 00:08:57.260
And that is something so much joy-giving,

00:08:57.285 --> 00:09:01.724
that the whole world can receive spirituality from you.

00:09:10.403 --> 00:09:13.671
Italians have to go everywhere,

00:09:13.696 --> 00:09:17.777
and to spread the message of love.

00:09:25.897 --> 00:09:29.703
Because you have the power of love.

00:09:33.139 --> 00:09:34.359
Of pure love.

00:09:36.466 --> 00:09:42.587
And this pure love will definitely transform many people.

00:09:48.255 --> 00:09:54.277
We have to change this world  which is full of problems.

00:09:58.765 --> 00:10:01.564
All alone, what can I do?

00:10:05.218 --> 00:10:08.906
They came to call Me to Turkey

00:10:08.931 --> 00:10:13.312
because they were having a financial crisis.

00:10:23.239 --> 00:10:27.230
And we had about 7,000 people in the hall.

00:10:31.005 --> 00:10:33.104
They are another great people.

00:10:53.980 --> 00:10:56.639
And you should be happy to know

00:10:56.664 --> 00:11:01.287
that within two days of My stay,

00:11:01.551 --> 00:11:06.674
the World Bank has given them 10 billion dollars!

00:11:34.597 --> 00:11:36.910
So, all your problems,

00:11:37.780 --> 00:11:42.995
whether physical, mental, emotional, financial,

00:11:43.020 --> 00:11:45.005
are to be solved.

00:11:55.053 --> 00:11:59.287
And many were cured also, during My stay there.

00:12:05.288 --> 00:12:08.114
But you are so developed spiritually

00:12:08.138 --> 00:12:12.284
that you can cure yourself and you can cure others also.

00:12:20.845 --> 00:12:23.438
This is something should happen,

00:12:23.463 --> 00:12:26.888
because I depend on you for this work.

00:12:35.744 --> 00:12:39.685
I love all of you very much, very much, very much.

00:12:44.780 --> 00:12:46.260
May God bless you all.

00:12:48.242 --> 00:12:50.635
But you have a responsibility.

00:12:52.847 --> 00:12:56.353
You have a duty to perform.

00:13:00.394 --> 00:13:07.512
Is to save people in this world which is getting into great problems.

00:13:15.187 --> 00:13:20.208
The main thing you should know that this is the Last Judgement.

00:13:24.791 --> 00:13:27.817
And you should take to spirituality.

00:13:31.234 --> 00:13:34.460
Let people be bad, let them be anything,

00:13:34.473 --> 00:13:37.381
but you try to make them good.

00:13:44.734 --> 00:13:49.666
I find lots of little children here who are born realised.

00:13:53.220 --> 00:13:54.913
And I love all of them.

00:13:56.487 --> 00:14:00.998
They’ll give you no problems, but on the contrary they’ll solve your problems.

00:14:06.136 --> 00:14:08.969
Because you Italians love children.

00:14:12.635 --> 00:14:17.178
So May God bless you all. Thank you for coming all the way here.
